title: #AskScullFriday Ep - 1 - You asked, I answered
description:
This Podcast was set up to help athletes of all levels, "I hope" It's me Stephen Scullion documenting my training / life, building to Tokyo 2020 Olympics.. "Hoping to qualify" I know I can do it, I believe I will do it, and this Podcast covers questions from the Twittersphere.. Submitted by you guys. #AskScullFriday 

PS - Guys, new Mic, rubbish... 

Support the show
